{"/service/ndnp/in/batch_in_archer_ver01/data/sn86058053/0051701719A/1930110101/0988.xml":{"full_text":"How long will you, as taxpayers -and voters of Lake county and the State\nof Indiana perpetuate the dangerous Republican policies existing in the\npublic offices of trust, permit existing conditions under the false mask\nof \u201cRepublican Party Regularity?\u201d\nI\nn ,ii\nThis is the most important political issue of the present campaign, and no\npolitical bosses, no political machine, no Republican Parly excuse will\nremedy this condition. Only the taxpayers and voters themselves can do\nthis on Tuesday, November 4.\nNo place can you find except in the state of Indiana, such misrule as is\nfound under the republican administration of Lake county and Indiana\npolitics. It is only in this county where yon find county commissioners\nunder indictment, township trustee in jail, township assessor recommend\ned for removal from office, mayor convicted, county treasurer mysterious\nly disappearing for a few weeks and state officials involved in \u201cbootleg\ngasoline scandal.\u201d\nRepublican Prosperity lias been a joke on the people of this state and\ncounty, even as in the whole United States. The \u201cgrafters\u201d have been\nable to satisfy their own personal greed and have allowed their thous\nands of constituents to plod along in dire need of the many necessities of\nlife. Remove them from office and remedy this condition!\nIf you, as a good citizen and taxpayer, are interested in the return of\nprosperity; if you are interested in the proper prosecution of law viola\ntors, NOW IS THE TIME when False Patriotism, Fa\n1\ni:se rrospeniy.\nHy\npocrisy in office, Corruption, Graft and Misrule of the Republican Party\nMachine must be stopped and replaced with Honesty, Sincerity and ike\nDesire to Serve,\nVOTE FOR A FULL DINNER PAIL VOTE THE STRAIGHT\nDEMOCRATIC TICKET\nGeneral Election November 4, 1930.\nCOLORED VOTERS OWE\nNOTHING TO THE\nREPUBLICANS\nThe Colored voter owes abso\nlutely nothing to the Republi\ncan Party In Indiana or in Lake\nCounty. Given power and put\ninto office time after time. Re\npublican Parly politicians have\ndone little aside from making\npromises which they have not\nkepi, and misleading and deceiv\ning the colored man.\nWithout the support of the Ne\ngro voters, the Republican party\nwould not he in office today;\nand yet the party has not given\none outstanding position to a\ncolored voter in either the State\nor County government. Not a\n\nsingle position paying as much\nor as little \u2014as $3,000 per\nyear has been given to a colored\nvoter anywhere In the State or\nCounty. The most the colored\nman has received has been the\ncrumbs from the table.\nout you have the power to cor\nrect this mistake,, to furnish such\nnegligence, and that power can\nhe exercised by every colored\nvoter at the polls next Tuesday.\nThe Democratic candidates have\npledged themselves, not only to\nclean house, but to give every\ngroup a square deal if elected to\noffice. Patronage will be evenly\ndistributed. Recognition will\nbe given to all. The rights of\nevery group will he respected.\nNo group in the county can hope\nto gain more than the colored\nvoter if the Democratic ticket\nwins, because the Democratic\ncandidates are anxious to prov e\ntheir worth if put into office.\nBut no group.in the county or\nslate need expect less if the Re\npublicans are again placed into\npower, because wSjat the G. O. P.\nhas failed to do during the last\n25 years they are hound to fail to\ndo in the next two or four years*\nYou can judge the future only\nby the past, and the past is re\nplete with empty promises nev\ner filled, widespread corruption\nand other evils which would be\ncured by a new administration\nand a new deal in polities.\n1 lie remedy is in your nanus.\nYou have absolutely nothing to\ngain by voting Republican, but\neverything to gain by uni ling\nwith the many thousands who\nhave voiced the demand for a\nnew administration, for a clean\nsweep in political affairs.","height":"25900","width":"20176"}}
